data.description: Discover this exquisite ranch-style residence, boasting 3 bedrooms, 1 elegantly designed bathroom, and the exciting possibility of an additional bathroom in the basement. Immerse yourself in the timeless allure of this home, where the floors were tastefully rejuvenated in 2023, harmonizing perfectly with the modernized bathroom. The roof, a steadfast guardian, was renewed in 2020. Adorning the bedrooms are genuine hardwood floors that exude both luxury and warmth. Descend into the basement to unveil a captivating expanse, a versatile canvas primed for entertainment and cherished moments.
